654
00:51:16,244 --> 00:51:17,563
Your answers.

655
00:51:18,764 --> 00:51:19,958
What are you willing to do?

656
00:51:20,364 --> 00:51:21,763
Anything and everything.

657
00:51:23,004 --> 00:51:25,154
That's worth drinking to, I'd imagine.

658
00:51:36,124 --> 00:51:37,921
Here's mud in your eye, pal.

659
00:51:42,164 --> 00:51:43,483
Good health.

660
00:51:48,164 --> 00:51:49,358
It's those things.

661
00:51:52,844 --> 00:51:53,959
Are they real?

662
00:51:55,724 --> 00:51:56,793
Of course they're real.

663
00:51:57,884 --> 00:51:59,522
Jesus Christ. I mean....

664
00:52:00,764 --> 00:52:01,879
Look at the pile.

665
00:52:02,524 --> 00:52:04,321
Look how high up they are.

666
00:52:05,204 --> 00:52:05,920
It looks like...

667
00:52:06,084 --> 00:52:10,123
- ...they were running from something.
- Okay. Don't touch, okay?

668
00:52:10,684 --> 00:52:14,723
Man, this thing is opened up
from the inside.

669
00:52:14,884 --> 00:52:16,363
Almost like it exploded.

670
00:52:17,324 --> 00:52:21,158
Looks like a scene out some sort
of holocaust painting, you know?

671
00:52:33,804 --> 00:52:34,998
Well....

672
00:52:40,364 --> 00:52:43,436
So, whatever killed them
is long gone, right?

673
00:52:43,604 --> 00:52:44,639
Millburn, Fifield.

674
00:52:44,804 --> 00:52:45,919
This is Prometheus.

675
00:52:46,084 --> 00:52:47,233
What is your position?

676
00:52:48,044 --> 00:52:49,762
Prometheus, this is Millburn.

677
00:52:50,044 --> 00:52:51,875
We are at 7-4-0...

678
00:52:52,044 --> 00:52:54,194
...1-4-7-7. Why?

679
00:52:54,364 --> 00:52:57,754
Just got a ping
about one click west of you.

680
00:52:57,924 --> 00:52:59,437
What do you mean "a ping"?

681
00:52:59,884 --> 00:53:01,476
Well, whatever...

682
00:53:01,644 --> 00:53:03,555
...that probe is picking up...

683
00:53:03,724 --> 00:53:04,839
...it's not dead.

684
00:53:05,004 --> 00:53:06,596
It's reading a life form.

685
00:53:06,804 --> 00:53:09,159
- What?
- Okay, what do you mean, "a life form"?

686
00:53:09,644 --> 00:53:11,157
Is it--? Is it moving?

687
