No, I don't think so.

688
00:53:14,044 --> 00:53:15,318
Captain, you're...

689
00:53:15,484 --> 00:53:16,963
...obviously not seeing...

690
00:53:17,124 --> 00:53:18,443
...what we're seeing here.

691
00:53:18,604 --> 00:53:20,754
If you were,
you wouldn't be talking about a ping.

692
00:53:20,924 --> 00:53:22,152
I know, boys.

693
00:53:22,484 --> 00:53:25,601
Your signal has been coming in
sporadically since the storm hit.

694
00:53:26,764 --> 00:53:28,197
That's no good to us down here!

695
00:53:29,684 --> 00:53:33,438
Is it--? Is it moving?
Are these things moving?

696
00:53:36,204 --> 00:53:39,002
No. No, it just disappeared, actually.

697
00:53:39,564 --> 00:53:40,599
Must be a glitch.

698
00:53:40,764 --> 00:53:43,153
What do you mean, "a glitch"?

699
00:53:43,324 --> 00:53:44,200
All right, boys.

700
00:53:45,244 --> 00:53:46,393
Sleep tight.

701
00:53:47,244 --> 00:53:48,677
Try not to bugger each other.

702
00:53:48,844 --> 00:53:50,755
Captain, what do you mean, "a glitch"?

703
00:53:51,364 --> 00:53:53,798
Millburn, what does he mean? Wait.

704
00:53:54,364 --> 00:53:55,797
Now, he said--

705
00:53:56,804 --> 00:53:59,398
- He said one click west, yeah?
- Yeah.

706
00:54:00,204 --> 00:54:01,432
Now, we....

707
00:54:01,604 --> 00:54:03,401
We don't want to check that out, do we?

708
00:54:03,564 --> 00:54:04,553
Shit, no.

709
00:54:04,724 --> 00:54:05,952
Where are we gonna go?

710
00:54:06,124 --> 00:54:07,079
East.

711
00:54:08,604 --> 00:54:09,832
Yeah, east.

712
00:54:10,004 --> 00:54:13,924
A fucking glitch, man.
