713
00:54:14,164 --> 00:54:18,237
Based on the behavior of the subject
in these holographic recordings...

714
00:54:18,404 --> 00:54:20,964
...we're attempting to identify
what caused the head...

715
00:54:21,124 --> 00:54:23,160
