from every man on Earth...

778
00:58:19,084 --> 00:58:20,995
...if I wanted to get laid, would it?

779
00:58:23,084 --> 00:58:24,517
Hey, Vickers.

780
00:58:24,684 --> 00:58:26,436
Hey, Vickers.

781
00:58:27,564 --> 00:58:29,316
I was wondering....

782
00:58:33,404 --> 00:58:34,757
