808
00:59:53,644 --> 00:59:54,599
Hey, baby.

809
00:59:55,364 --> 00:59:56,035
Hey.

810
00:59:57,004 --> 00:59:58,119
Come in, Prometheus.

811
00:59:58,444 --> 01:00:01,880
